	   <tr><td colspan=2>I play a Barb Shaman, I want to leave Halas and go be with my buds around freeport or perhaps near crushbone. My question is, is there any place to apply my training points other than at my guild in Halas? Will I be welcome in Grobb or Oggok? Is there a shaman in the freeport sewers? Please help.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;          Thank You in Advance,<br>                Pimplefarmer<br>              Barbarian Shaman<br>                  Veeshan<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
