	   <tr><td colspan=2>54th Level Barb Shaman on Rallos Zek here.<br>I just want to say that I think its a good idea to use 2 hand blunt early on in your levels. All the way up to 25 where you can still melee a bit.You should however work up your piercing at about this point. All level 25 and below shamans should go get the Ebon War spear to start practicing piercing with. <br><br>I normally only use Barbarian Spiritualist hammer +13wis and a Howling Harpoon +6wis +40mana in my range slot. Giving me about a +21 to wiz. Not bad for going for 2hblunt. However your probably not going to have a weapon like this till way later, so get yourself a Spear and shield a book, whatever, and use the 2hblunt when you want to step in and mix it up a bit, and when its time to med and be a healer put on the shield and piercer for the extra mana. Not like you cant carry almost as much as a warrior. <br><br>my 2cents<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
