	   <tr><td colspan=2>If it were me I would not kyte. Kytting is not something that shaman excell at.&nbsp;&nbsp;I think you are much better of casting dots and meleeing.  Note you can not kill yellow cons if you intend to melee.  <br><br>Buff yourself up, and cast your slow spell on the mob, run if you like and cast sickness based dot and then poison dots.  Then melee the mob while the dots work.  <br><br>Note dots only do 75% of there damage if the mob is moving while dotted.  <br><br>Shaman have good melee skill and need not be afraid to mix it up with the mob<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
